Usage: fix_drc_with_patch [-help] [<area>] [-include_passive_fill]
                          [-layer_range <string>]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<area>                    # route area (box, optional)
-include_passive_fill     # combo commnad to do passive fill after drc fixing
                          # (bool, optional)
-layer_range <string>     # for -fix_drc within lowerLayer:upperLayer
                          # (string, optional)